org.livingdoc.repositories.rest

Class RESTRepositoryFactory

  • org.livingdoc.repositories.rest.RESTRepositoryFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentRepositoryFactory<T>

    public class RESTRepositoryFactory
implements DocumentRepositoryFactory<T>

    This Factory is used to create a RESTRepository. This Factory must be specified in the livingdoc.yml to use the REST Repository. For more details about the {@see RESTRepository} see it's documentation.
